{"tid":2495113,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男生被控理大串謀暴動 今獲准以現金及人事擔保共25萬保釋 需每天報到","createTime":"2021-04-19T03:59:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T10:38:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a3e819b1ef5de1a58f7ca260f99ceacdea977f7e","tid":2495113,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:59:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15100&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=46bfb26b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15100</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院第七庭 #申請保釋<br />\n#張慧玲法官 #1111理大 <br />\n👤姜(22) 🛑已還押逾1個月 <br />\n<br />\n控罪：串謀暴動<br />\n姜手足被控於或約於2019年11月11日與11月14日（包括首尾兩日），在香港串謀與其他不知名的人於香港理工大學參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n🟢考慮雙方陳詞後，法官准予申請人保釋，保釋條件如下：<br />\n<br />\n1) 保釋金$100,000，父親人事擔保$100,000，女友父親人事擔保$50,000<br />\n2) 宵禁 22:00 - 08:00<br />\n3) 不得離境<br />\n4) 須交出所有旅遊證件<br />\n5) 居住在報稱住址<br />\n6) 每天前往警署報到1次<br />\n7) 不得直接或間接接觸控方證人<br />\n<br />\n💛感謝旁聽師提供資訊💛"},{"pid":"87f6cc0ba2b6880a3407ed23508c823e83312b2a","tid":2495113,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268b5bade19d05641861e60dd41224ed825defba","tid":2495113,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:00:05.000Z","msg":"呢個又好嚴"},{"pid":"f5ccd21e2a0547c27cf3a318fc93d2508cb8f6a9","tid":2495113,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184f942be644bce32a25f526c8f66828777f86ac","tid":2495113,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f1a279bb57d08cdfed26ccb53aaf7609af2de7","tid":2495113,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4369698af992a012b10fa6ff0ed12ed7eeb48566","tid":2495113,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f49b1593d12d3993f5b0f6284fd20b3d3e1fd3d","tid":2495113,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9a761d937e85b6b7bf052063f0c21447b38b4a","tid":2495113,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"268b5bade19d05641861e60dd41224ed825defba","tid":2495113,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:00:05.000Z","msg":"呢個又好嚴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:32:50.000Z","msg":"上高院申請保釋係會嚴少少<br />\n因為裁判官本身拒絕保釋<br />\n要說服高院批就要提出高啲條件先有機會保得番出嚟"},{"pid":"312d64ed005aab5f12740e5ad3333e4886352138","tid":2495113,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:38:28.000Z","msg":"被告姜與另外四人被控一項串謀暴動罪，涉於約前年11月11日至14日期間，串謀不知名人士於香港理工大學參與暴動。裁判官<span class=\"red\">鄭念慈</span>早前拒絕批准被告保釋。案件將在區域法院審理，本月27日在區院提訊。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/3QJOS4HLZFHARDGI5WUO7V6S2I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2F3QJOS4HLZFHARDGI5WUO7V6S2I%2F&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=177e3ed1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?